Valid values: 7 to 730.', example='7'),
  ownerAccount?: string(name='OwnerAccount'),
  ownerId?: long(name='OwnerId'),
  preferredBackupPeriod?: string(name='PreferredBackupPeriod', description='The backup cycle. Valid values:

